{"tid":215343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影帝劈價賣玉墜 低價遊長城有餘興節目","createTime":"2017-04-24T11:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T16:04:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0549cfe05e4f7313a5111fb49eca0688008ca5b","tid":215343,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"2017/4/23 下午10:00:29<br />\n【「影帝」劈價賣玉墜】<br />\n【低價遊長城有餘興節目】<br />\n<br />\n有內地記者最近「放蛇」，參加低價長城遊，看看不良旅遊業者有些甚麼新招騙遊客。<br />\n<br />\n基本不變的是以 50 元先騙上車，跟著就反口叫價，要付 210 元才能做「好漢」。<br />\n<br />\n到回程時，導遊借口車壞，把旅客效在一間玉石店，讓各人休息，其實就是請君入甕。<br />\n<br />\n記者發現，店內會有自稱少東的「影帝」，看準人類貪小便宜、似是而非的惻隱之心，軟硬兼施推銷他的玉器，同行者不少定力不足，相繼奉上一、二千元，買走「影帝」的劈貨。<br />\n<br />\n＃有線新聞　＃長城　＃北京　＃放蛇　有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/662612467264158/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F662612467264158%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e0729ebc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/662612467264158/</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4a49042d3a0f3e4147816044015591af2bfd7a","tid":215343,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52965924e6c7e98aada8fe1ddaaceeffe0b57fe2","tid":215343,"uid":56531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T17:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aa88954b616559ce2498dee0eb85